What's wrong with this picture
========================================================
"You can totally generalize the results of this Tweet data analysis to the rest of the population!"

**Strong strong** selection bias of who signs up to Twitter and who tweets what.  The sample is non-random so the sample is not representative of the population as a hold, rather the biased sample.

Don't EVER be fooled into thinking this, nor ever write this.



