Create Twitter OAS Authentication
========================================================

We are getting digital permission to open the Twitter pipeline for our uses.  Just like every major media outlet on earth.

* Install `twitteR` package
* Check package's [GitHub page](https://github.com/hadley/stringr)
* Create a Twitter application at [http://dev.twitter.com](http://dev.twitter.com). Make sure to give the app read, write and direct message authority.
* Note the "API key", "API secret", "Access token", and "Access token secret".
Install development version of [https://github.com/hadley/stringr](https://github.com/hadley/stringr)


